PRO AND ENTERPRISE TIERS - COMMERCIAL LICENSE

A valid purchased license key is required to use Pro or Enterprise features.
These features include but are not limited to:

  Pro: SSH tunneling, Readonly connection mode, Edit JSON, Upload binary,
  Download binary.

  Enterprise: All Pro features plus Cluster and Sentinel connections,
  --readonly-connections/-r flag.

Terms:

  1. A license key is required for each installation (per seat).
  2. License keys are non-transferable.
  3. All payments are non-refundable.
  4. License validation requires internet access.
  5. Unauthorized use of Pro or Enterprise features without a valid license
     is prohibited.

For pricing, trial information, and purchasing, please refer to the README
at https://github.com/patrikx3/redis-ui#tier-feature-policy or contact
support@corifeus.com.
